<view class="page results-page"><view class="search-header-wrap"><view class="search-input-box"><text class="search-glass-icon">🔍</text><input class="header-search-input" placeholder="输入关键词搜索承运商" placeholder-style="color:#94a3b8" bindconfirm="{{a}}" value="{{b}}" bindinput="{{c}}"/></view><button class="primary-btn search-confirm-btn" bindtap="{{d}}">搜索</button></view><view class="route-details-banner"><view class="route-text-line"><text class="route-point">{{e}}</text><text class="route-connector-arrow">⇄</text><text class="route-point">{{f}}</text></view></view><view class="sub-filter-pills-row"><view class="{{['sub-filter-pill', g && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{h}}"> 大板运输 </view><view class="{{['sub-filter-pill', i && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{j}}"> 全程小板 </view></view><view wx:if="{{k}}" class="carrier-count-summary"> 已筛选出 {{l}} 家承运线路 </view><view wx:if="{{m}}" class="empty-results-v2"><view class="empty-visual">📭</view><text class="empty-title">暂无匹配的承运商</text><view class="empty-action-card"><button class="primary-btn empty-quick-btn" bindtap="{{n}}">返回首页调整条件</button><text class="empty-action-desc">建议您更换起始城市、目的地或关键词后重新查询。</text></view></view><block wx:elif="{{o}}"><view wx:for="{{p}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="f" class="section carrier-card-v2"><view class="carrier-card-header"><view class="carrier-title-block"><view class="carrier-name-title-row"><text class="carrier-company-name">{{item.a}}</text></view><view class="rating-and-tags"><text class="status-tag status-success mini-tag">认证承运商</text><text class="status-tag status-info mini-tag">{{item.b}}</text></view></view></view><view class="carrier-services-block"><view wx:for="{{item.c}}" wx:for-item="srv" wx:key="f" class="service-price-row"><text class="service-name-label">{{srv.a}}</text><view class="service-meta-right"><text wx:if="{{srv.b}}" class="service-time-lbl">约最快 {{srv.c}} 送达</text><text class="{{['service-price-val', srv.e && 'highlight']}}">{{srv.d}}</text></view></view></view><view class="carrier-actions-block"><button class="secondary-btn contact-action-btn" bindtap="{{item.d}}">电话联系</button><button class="primary-btn create-order-action-btn" bindtap="{{item.e}}"> 发起订单 </button></view></view></block><view wx:if="{{q}}" class="loading-box"><text class="loading-spinner">⏳</text><text class="loading-text">正在全网帮您寻找承运商...</text></view></view>